Producer: Matthew E. Chausse, Benni Diez, Liam O'Donnell, Colin Strause, Greg Strause
Production Co: Media Finance Capital, Mirabelle Pictures Productions, Fasten Films, Artbox
Synopsis: When a virus threatens to turn friendly alien hybrids against humans, Capt. Rose Corley and her team of elite soldiers embark on a mission to an extraterrestrial world to save what's left of mankind.
Title: Skylines
